coltrane at his most powerful although `` a love supreme '' is generally regarded as coltrane 's most emotional album , `` sun ship '' tops it in intensity and passion . the music is volatile , from lush mccoy tyner passages and coltrane themes , to elvin jones 's furious percussion and coltrane 's atonal improvisation . coltrane 's solos on the title track and `` amen '' are guaranteed to give you goosebumps , if you `` get '' his later stuff